OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FTurning
OL,6,Fincreasingly wet this evening with
OL,7,Fperiods of rain, this heavy and
OL,8,Fpersistent for a time, with perhaps an
OL,9,Fisolated rumble of thunder. Gradually
OL,10,Fturning drier overnight but showers
OL,11,Fremain possible, these locally heavy.
OL,12,FStaying mild and rather humid.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FHeavy and thundery showers
OL,15,Fdeveloping quite widely with hail,
OL,16,Flightning and torrential downpours in
OL,17,Fplaces, especially in southern coastal
OL,18,Fregions. Feeling rather warm but
OL,19,Fbreezier than on Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
